1 Registration Login

As a user, I want to login using my social media profiles or private emal
As a system, I want to validate the registration & login process using Firebase Authentication 

2 Profile {Interior Design}
As a user, I want to personalize/design my user profile
As a system, I want to display the user profile -- 

2a Camera/Gallery
As a system, I want to support image uploads from the device gallery or camera

2b App Store
As a system, I want to support purchase of Sticker Packs

2c Background color
As a system, I want to change the background color of a user profile via a color wheel

3 Content 
As a user, I want to upload images or video 
As a system, I want to display user uploaded images or video in a newsfeed stream for all users to see 
{filters apply by geo-locations or partners admins}

3a Content Live Stream
As a user, I want to create a live stream 
As a system, I want to support a live stream event 
{in app purchases}

